        <h1 itemprop="headline">SNP activist 'killed over child sex files'</h1>

        
                <h3>A FIREBRAND SNP activist who died in mysterious circumstances was to expose a paedophile ring that would have brought down the Government, it was claimed last night.</h3>
        
        <div class="panel new">
            <div class="publish-info">
                                <div class="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author">
                    By
                                        <a href="/search/Paula+Murray?s=Paula+Murray&b=1"><span itemprop="name">Paula Murray</span></a>
                                                        </div>
                                <div class="dates">
                    <meta itemprop="datepublished" content="2014-11-30T00:01:00Z" />
                    <time pubdate datetime="2014-11-30T00:01:00Z">
                        <span>PUBLISHED: </span><span>00:01, Sun, Nov 30, 2014</span>
                    </time>
                                    </div>
            </div>
            
            <!--OVOLABS_4 END-->
